# ğŸ¥’â¡ğŸ“„ cuke2conf â€” Publish Cucumber Reports to Confluence

[![Build](https://github.com/sjacobs/cuke2conf/actions/workflows/build.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/sjacobs/cuke2conf/actions/workflows/build.yml)
